  "lyrics": "I think there's something to say, ay Did you know that you're not the thing I used to see before Something new, I don't like the devil's alone Sittin' here, sittin' there more with me Sittin' there, sittin' there more with you You got this whole heritage And you know your bloodline to boot Yeah, you're rare, you're legendary Hell, you're mythical to me You're mythical to me, you're more than rare You're more than legendary You're mythical to me, you're mythical to me I like your concepts and concepts I like the way you respond to things that I said I like every voice inside your head That tells you the things that you wanna do Instead of what you did back then I can see that you change, huh? I can see that you roll lovely I can just see, man I wonder what's up with that ring though Ay, fam, tell me You're more than rare You're more than legendary You're mythical to me You're more than rare, more than legendary You're mythical to me, you're mythical to me More than rare, more than legendary You're mythical to me What if we just go out for a little bit of coffee? Conversate with the wind I like your opinion, I like your manner Come and join my team, girl There ain't no get better Don't wanna be about anything but friendship Maybe cooperation, something professional You know, you're just amazing And I had to tell you, I had to tell someone Because you're more than rare You're more than legendary You're mythical to me Ay, you're more than rare You're more than legendary You're mythical Ay, you're more than rare You're more than legendary You're mythical to me, mythical to me So maybe take a little second, check it out I got many different cousins in the world Maybe compensate on this No reason to think it's not anything but what we say it would be So come over, have some coffee with me Talk about the next chapter, the next level of reality Ay, you're more than rare You're more than legendary You're mythical to me You're more than rare",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 22.399999618530273,
      "text": "I think there's something to say, ay Did you know that you're not the thing I",
      "start": 14.899999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 26.8799991607666,
      "text": "used to see before Something new, I don't like the devil's alone",
      "start": 22.600000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 31.899999618530273,
      "text": "Sittin' here, sittin' there more with me Sittin' there, sittin' there more with you",
      "start": 27.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 36.2599983215332,
      "text": "You got this whole heritage And you know your bloodline to boot",
      "start": 31.899999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 43.279998779296875,
      "text": "Yeah, you're rare, you're legendary Hell, you're mythical to me",
      "start": 36.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 49.540000915527344,
      "text": "You're mythical to me, you're more than rare You're more than legendary",
      "start": 43.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 54.29999923706055,
      "text": "You're mythical to me, you're mythical to me",
      "start": 49.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 59.18000030517578,
      "text": "I like your concepts and concepts I like the way you respond to things that I said",
      "start": 54.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 62.79999923706055,
      "text": "I like every voice inside your head That tells you the things that you wanna do",
      "start": 59.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 64.30000305175781,
      "text": "Instead of what you did back then",
      "start": 62.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 69.05999755859375,
      "text": "I can see that you change, huh? I can see that you roll lovely",
      "start": 64.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 72.37999725341797,
      "text": "I can just see, man I wonder what's up with that ring though",
      "start": 69.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 75.30000305175781,
      "text": "Ay, fam, tell me You're more than rare",
      "start": 72.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 81.94000244140625,
      "text": "You're more than legendary You're mythical to me",
      "start": 75.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 91.72000122070312,
      "text": "You're more than rare, more than legendary You're mythical to me, you're mythical to me",
      "start": 81.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 100.63999938964844,
      "text": "More than rare, more than legendary You're mythical to me",
      "start": 92.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 104.05999755859375,
      "text": "What if we just go out for a little bit of coffee?",
      "start": 101.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 107.33999633789062,
      "text": "Conversate with the wind I like your opinion, I like your manner",
      "start": 104.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 110.18000030517578,
      "text": "Come and join my team, girl There ain't no get better",
      "start": 107.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 115.23999786376953,
      "text": "Don't wanna be about anything but friendship Maybe cooperation, something professional",
      "start": 110.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 118.80000305175781,
      "text": "You know, you're just amazing And I had to tell you, I had to tell someone",
      "start": 115.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 123.41999816894531,
      "text": "Because you're more than rare You're more than legendary",
      "start": 118.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 126.91999816894531,
      "text": "You're mythical to me",
      "start": 123.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 132.8000030517578,
      "text": "Ay, you're more than rare You're more than legendary",
      "start": 126.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 135.86000061035156,
      "text": "You're mythical",
      "start": 133.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 141.66000366210938,
      "text": "Ay, you're more than rare You're more than legendary",
      "start": 136.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 146.75999450683594,
      "text": "You're mythical to me, mythical to me",
      "start": 141.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 149.52000427246094,
      "text": "So maybe take a little second, check it out",
      "start": 146.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 152.25999450683594,
      "text": "I got many different cousins in the world",
      "start": 149.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 154.0399932861328,
